Responsibility

Use of SLANG-Computation in real-world systems is entirely at the user’s own responsibility.

This reference implementation provides:

deterministic structural computation resolution
outcome emergence from structure
safe handling of incomplete/conflicting structure

It does not provide:

general-purpose computation guarantees
program correctness guarantees outside defined structure
system-level execution guarantees
safety-critical assurances
regulatory or compliance guarantees
operational guarantees

