Closing Statement

SLANG-Computation explores a simple but fundamental idea:

Computation correctness can emerge deterministically from structure, without execution flow, control flow, or prescribed sequencing.

It is released openly to encourage:

independent validation
real-world testing
safe experimentation

SLANG-Computation is offered as a minimal reference implementation of that possibility.
